window.bookSummaryJSON = "Take one bored princess. Make her the seventh daughter in a very proper royal family. Have her run away. <p>Add one powerful, fascinating, dangerous dragon.</p> <p>Princess Cimerone has never met anyone (or anything) like the dragon Kazul. But then, she's never met a witch, a jinn, a death-dealing talking bird or a stone prince either.</p> <p>Princess Cimerone ran away to find some excitement.</p> <p>She's found plenty.</p>"; 
